<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    /* Navbar */
    header {
      background-color: #333;
      padding: 1em 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    
    .nav-links, .auth-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1em;
    }
    
    .nav-links li {
      list-style: none;
    }
    
    .nav-links a, .auth-links a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.5em 1em;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .nav-links a:hover, .auth-links a:hover {
      background-color: #555;
    }
    
    /* Sections */
    section {
      padding: 4em 2em;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    
    #home {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    
    .home-img {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 1em;
    }
    
    /* Contact Form */
    #contact-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1em;
    }
    
    #contact-form input, #contact-form textarea {
      padding: 0.5em;
      font-size: 1em;
      width: 100%;
    }
    
    button[type="submit"] {
      background-color: #333;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.5em;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    button[type="submit"]:hover {
      background-color: #555;
    }
    .navbar .fa{
      color: white;
      font-size: 2rem;
    
    }
    
      </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>We are a company dedicated to providing the best web solutions.</p>
        <p>Our team consists of skilled developers and designers ready to bring your ideas to life.</p>
      </section>
   
      <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>